{"tid":1965457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駕駛艙內 機師不准戴口罩","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T13:23:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0f8934582cd6b22614d13ecb7d60f44c813528","tid":1965457,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200409/Z4C5RVHBL4MGOWTXFI62DA5I4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200409%2FZ4C5RVHBL4MGOWTXFI62DA5I4I%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVdw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=a4ab9f35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200409%2FZ4C5RVHBL4MGOWTXFI62DA5I4I%2F&h=338e4d58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200409/Z4C5RVHBL4MGOWTXFI62DA5I4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n駕駛艙內 機師不准戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200409/large/1586362477_6045.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200409%2Flarge%2F1586362477_6045.gif&h=8c8e8c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有機師指機師其實十分高危，因他們在機艙內不能戴口罩。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n航空公司的航班大大減少，對僅餘還有上班的員工，被指為削減成本而防疫裝備不足。早前國泰一度派沒有中層熔噴布的口罩，也不容許空姐戴眼罩。有空姐指除了自備口罩外，也沒有甚麼能夠做，只能祈求航機上沒有染病乘客，事後自我隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n港航空姐：得KFC嗰種手套<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：股神投降 急掟航空股<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港龍空姐指出，公司會派發藍色的保護衣、口罩、眼罩、手套。至於財困多時的香港航空，空姐王小姐指公司沒有提供防疫用具，「公司冇錢呀，得KFC嗰隻藍色手套，口罩都冇提供；所以喺架飛機度，會見到空姐戴住唔同款式嘅口罩、眼罩」。<br />\n<br />\n機師不需要接觸乘客，留在獨立的駕駛艙，外界以為很安全，不過有港人機師指出，機師其實十分高危，因他們在機艙內不能戴口罩，「因為有條例規定，機師必須在十秒內戴上氧氣罩呼吸，如果戴口罩，會阻慢戴氧氣罩速度」。同行機師、副機師關在同一狹小空間裏，如果一人受感染，另一人可說一定會被傳染；港人機師擔心，很多外國機師的防疫意識低，受感染機會較大。<br />\n<br />\n不少航空從業員批評政府罔顧他們的安全：「需要我哋時就講要顧及經濟，遲遲唔封關，令到前線人員要接觸遊客，變成高危工作；但又一啲補貼畀航空公司員工都冇，即使連醫護都唔夠裝備，所有資源畀晒警隊，個個行業都喺度捱緊，只有警隊無憂無慮，還要我們相信政府嗎？」"},{"pid":"0d0c5ef335f79d2d07f66ebe2589dc270e7f73ca","tid":1965457,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75ce808e1de04c08d2d95f195405a73f8d43e203","tid":1965457,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢地戴囉<br />\n佢地接觸得最多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752a48f6d21d5662e9cf1c9143849f959aa58fb5","tid":1965457,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:05:58.000Z","msg":"戴口罩點call ATC呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1b94c5b001971bbc8f2beccfc6aad35a518457","tid":1965457,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"每次個駕駛倉有無消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f5b7804e7ce24729d40fdc9ef77ec8937a27b","tid":1965457,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b1b94c5b001971bbc8f2beccfc6aad35a518457","tid":1965457,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"每次個駕駛倉有無消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:13:31.000Z","msg":"最污糟就係cockpit d panel<br />\n<br />\n十年無人抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39be792bcd3783cb8e7c979be18dda8fa900ea27","tid":1965457,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c79f5b7804e7ce24729d40fdc9ef77ec8937a27b","tid":1965457,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"